label: Marital
desc: marital : marital status (categorical: "married","divorced","single"; note: "divorced" means divorced or widowed)

label: Balance
desc: balance: average yearly balance, in euros (numeric)

label: Day
desc: day: last contact day of the month (numeric)

label: Month
desc: month: last contact month of year (categorical: "jan", "feb", "mar", ..., "nov", "dec")

label: Duration
desc: duration: last contact duration, in seconds (numeric)

label: Campaign
desc: campaign: number of contacts performed during this campaign and for this client (numeric, includes last contact)

label: Pdays
desc: pdays: number of days that passed by after the client was last contacted from a previous campaign (numeric, -1 means client was not previously contacted)

label: Previous
desc: revious: number of contacts performed before this campaign and for this client (numeric)

label: Poutcome
desc: poutcome: outcome of the previous marketing campaign (categorical: "unknown","other","failure","success")

label: Subscription
desc: y - has the client subscribed a term deposit? (binary: "yes","no")
